findings.title: Low issues in DoS with block gas limit
findings.description: The contract may be vulnerable to Denial of Service (DoS) attacks due to the block gas limit.

findings.title: Owner privileges
findings.description: The owner has excessive privileges to change critical contract settings such as tax and liquidity fee, maximum transaction amount, and exclusion from fees.
findings.function: setTaxFeePercent, setLiquidityFeePercent, setMaxTxPercent, excludeFromFee, includeInFee, etc.
